name: Fungi Greeting Card & Magnet of the Hawaiian Rainforest Wild Mushrooms
description:
My Photographs are inspired by the beauty of the Hawaiian Rainforest.

This is my "Marty Feldman Incarnation Greeting Card & Magnet"

This 4" x 5" Greeting Card & 4" x 5" Magnet makes a unique gift & keepsake.  

My Greeting Card is Printed on Premium Glossy cardstock which is framable.  And the Beautiful Fridge or filing cabinet magnet will
enhance your interior with the beauty of nature.

name: Doughboy Greeting Card With a Fridge Magnet on the Inside!
description:
Frameable Doughboy Greeting card which includes a Fridge Magnet
as an added gift.  My painting was done in Arcylic Paint
Size of Card 4" x 5" Glossey Card and the size of  4 x 5  Magnet
(this is a nice gift card  which has a magnet inside when you open the inside of the  card their is a magnet of the doughboy art to put on your fridge)

The Inside says: "Just Poppin' to say..."

A perfect card to send to keep in touch with a special gift magnet inside

My father Jim Jordan directed the first Pillsbury Commercials before they had computers.   I remember visiting his studio in Hollywood and saw hundreds of clay doughboys lined up a row in a glass case.  These were used to create the old animated flims.  And YES, I DID get permission for this Rendition / Interpretation of the Doughboy from General Mills / Pillsbury and have signed a formal contract with their legal department.
This makes a wonderful keepsake and is nice to frame or give with a gift of homemade cookies.

name: Purple Sprout / Hawaii Rain Forest Small keepsake Magnet
description:
Hawaii Rain Forest Magnet.  Approximate size is same size as a business card 3 inch x 2 inch.   Coming soon is a larger size magnet of the same design. The beauty of Hawaii has been inspired me to take hundreds of Photographs of Hawaii and the Rain Forest

This Magnet make a wonderful keepsake to put in a small frame or put on your fridge or filing cabinet.
